{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ed19f9343d","title":"通县发现五十六起买卖土地事件","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"62fe6a6ff6","index":0,"year":1963,"month":3,"day":19,"articleId":"ed19f9343d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"45ec15172b","type":"title","text":"通县发现五十六起买卖土地事件","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"ed19f9343d"},{"id":"3a7ddcf2c4","type":"paragraph","text":"北京郊区通县在宣传贯彻“六十条”当中，揭发出五十六起社员买卖土地事件。1962年上半年最多，约达四十余起。买卖的土地有五十起是房基地，四起是开荒地，两起是自留地。买卖地的数量一般在半亩左右，多的一亩八分，少的二、三分。地价高的每亩达一千余元。（编自北京市委“简报”）","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"ed19f9343d"},{"id":"325b9ada15","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：根据1963年3月19日新华社《内部参考》。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"ed19f9343d"}],"page":{"id":"f6ad372a94","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"ed19f9343d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}